FBIS3-5366 "dreas044_c_94032" FBIS-EAS-94-044 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Mar 1994 North Korea Kim Chong-il Provides Equipment for Food Factory SK0503044794 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0416 GMT 5 Mar 94 SK0503044794 Pyongyang KCNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Pyongyang, March 5 (KCNA) -- The dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il showed deep solicitude to the Pyongyang children's foodstuff factory for the rising generation. He recently provided the factory with new conditions for the improvement of the quality of foodstuffs for children and increase the quantity at the factory. After building the excellent production bases of foodstuffs for children in Pyongyang, he indicated long ago the orientation and way of supplying different kinds of foodstuffs good for the health and growth of children in large quantities, sent a lot of equipment to the factory and took measures for the production, management and operation of the factory.
